{
  "texts": [
    "• What color is yak milk?",
    "By inspection of consistency matrices, we found that LLama3 has a hard time classifying elements of class Entity that refer to colors (exceptions are the second and fourth samples that belong to subclass \"other\").",
    "We hypothesize that all questions pertaining to colors might be problematic for LLama3, hence we refine the prompt by adding \"Note that questions about colors count as elements of class Entity.\".",
    "Once more, this prompt correction is enough to significantly improve the classification of the three examples about color, moving from a number of correct predictions over 30 rephrasings of [0, 4, 3, 15, 0] to [30, 4, 30, 15, 30].",
    "Inconsistency of high-sensitivity samples is a good proxy for their \"classification hardness\", because their individual distributions p τ differ a lot from the others."
  ]
}